592
00:36:15,630 --> 00:36:16,430
Guo Baokun has stopped using

593
00:36:16,430 --> 00:36:17,560
a servant for a long time.

594
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,630
I see.

595
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:19,710
