687
00:39:48,230 --> 00:39:49,520
You should know what kind of a person Ruoruo is.

688
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,430
She won't be so rude.

689
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:56,800
You...

690
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,840
