691
00:40:35,430 --> 00:40:37,190
Write down that poem.

692
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:16,600
Lady Ye, why are you standing here?

693
00:41:16,910 --> 00:41:17,760
I...

694
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:20,630
