714
00:42:25,520 --> 00:42:26,760
Li Hongcheng gave it to me.

715
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:29,320
Do you believe me now?

716
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:31,000
How can you be...

717
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,150
